Community Flare Addon for World of Warcraft (Dragonflight) v10.1.5
- Helps track Community Members from your Community in Battlegrounds.
- Also helps to make Queing up for Battlegrounds more pleasant.
- Fixes some annoyances by the standard UI.

Installation:
- Simply drag the "Community_Flare" folder into your {World of Warcraft}\_retail_\Addons folder.

Notes:
- Check changes.txt to see what's been updated each revision.
